PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 2009-985 of June 16, 2009, by replacing the words “Robert Orr as High Commissioner for Canada to the United Republic of Tanzania, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Seychelles and the Union of the Comoros; and” with the words “Robert Orr as High Commissioner for Canada to the United Republic of Tanzania, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Seychelles and as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Union of the Comoros; and”.
